description:
On an all new episode of Unqualified, Anna and Sim talk with Brittany Snow (PITCH PERFECT 3) about the Pitch Perfect franchise (4:45), hypothetical murder scenarios (8:25), and play a new segment called On A First Date (11:30) and a round of How Would You Proceed? (25:20)

Later they call Kelsey (38:00) who's worried about seeing her ex-boyfriend at her friends upcoming wedding and Kristen (53:15) who has an old flame trying to reconnect with her years after breaking up. Tune in!
